column5: Weve many places to go tomorrow so we opened our gifts tonght... and I got what I wanted.. a very happy family.  Thanks to everyone, merry xmas I hope its all you want it to be as well.  Have a great holiday!!
Merry Christmas TJ... to you, Monique and the kids! I like you have the only thing we need... everyone happy and the 3 young adults not even arguing today ! lol
LOL Wayne Kids are on thier own here. Very peaceful and enjoying our time.   Have a great festive time boss.
Merry Christmas to you aswell TJ, and Monique, Avery, Jaden & Muskie.  I should be getting off to bed tho.  Christmas morning comes early  Merry Christmas all  Joey
Best wishes for the holiday season to you and yours TJ
Merry Christmas TJ,  You can't buy a gift like that...  Glad you are showing it off ...  Hope everyone has a safe and happy holiday!  Merry Christmas  Jen

Well .. Santa JUST got done writing his replies here in Etobicoke ... and is off to bed ...er his next stop... I cant agree more TJ ... Merry christmas to you and Monique ...and ALL our good little OFC'ers
Merry Merry, Ho Ho Ho...  Have a fun and safe day today all!!!  Maureen

Merry Christmas, we had a nice big Christmas Eve dinner last night and i got to see lot's of family, it was a great time and it felt so perfect. Well now i got to sit here at this computer and hold myself from going downstairs....."come on mom and dad, GET UP ALREADY ITS CHRISTMAS!!!"   Have a safe and merry Christmas!

A very nice quiet Christmas eve here. A special dinner, Sue's favorite food, fresh stone crab driven up directly from FL. by a good friend. Lots of phone calls with family and friends and some nice background Christmas music. We would have rather been with our kids but.... well, we all know what the weather was like yesterday, if it isn't burried in snow, it is covered in ice.  Wishing each and everyone of you a Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year!
You are now, the richest man alive! Merry Ho Ho, from Dan
Back at ya boss.  Sorry I missed you.  I'll try you later today.
Tj I hope all is well and ya can get out of the driveway I here ya have alot of snow this year. Merry Christmas to you and the family and a happy new year.
